>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">图 3： 仿真环境 (a-c) 和真实环境 (d-f) 中渐进式奖励对比图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">效率优势显著</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">效率方面，在图 4 中，对于 LIBERO 长时序任务，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">初始模型 One-shot SFT 成功率仅 17.3%，SRPO 仅用 219 步即提升至 98.6%</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，相比同期 GRPO，性能提升 15.3%，相较 150k 步的 full-shot SFT 模型性能提升 12.9%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503522399\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7296137339055794\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"466\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"375\" data-backh=\"274\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=493354a6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicGEnDGkLkVWt55aMUZK7UEnrRNA9pKKvtIibFeL9WchdibbysriajAgGe69QppZzAoZ56QaTibZWia2AQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">图 4： SRPO 与 GRPO 的训练效率比较。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">奖励建模真机实测</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们还尝试将 SRPO 的奖励建模应用到真实环境中，如图 5 所示，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">在五个真机任务上，开源模型</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503522415\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7272727272727273\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"44\" style=\"width:25px;height:20px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5900c008&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicGEnDGkLkVWt55aMUZK7UEcaDhibayY7lMqiboqtKnZ3wS7wkicvNTnFuE4oXdbb10Sp9xfAW3dSlibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">和&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503522415\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7272727272727273\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"44\" style=\"width:25px;height:20px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5900c008&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicGEnDGkLkVWt55aMUZK7UEcaDhibayY7lMqiboqtKnZ3wS7wkicvNTnFuE4oXdbb10Sp9xfAW3dSlibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">-fast 成功率相对 SFT 分别提升 66.8% 和 86.7%</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503522400\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6822742474916388\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"598\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"394\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=427cd6b2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicGEnDGkLkVWt55aMUZK7UEIyr3XFIr4AhmP2jU4YqClz5hMCOVMj3uiaQoICegibRU30LIAEo0GmrA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">图 5： 相较于 SFT 基线，SRPO 奖励构建方法在真实世界任务上成功率有显著提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">激发创造性：让机器人学会「自主寻路」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此外，我们发现 SRPO 训练后，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">模型能够自主探索出多种专家轨迹中不存在的新路径与抓取姿态</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，如图 6 所示。说明 SRPO 不仅能提升成功率，更能激发机器人超越示范、自主探索新的解决策略。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503522401\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.35374149659863946\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"588\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"204\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fac05178&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicGEnDGkLkVWt55aMUZK7UEs5EGd3uic6SnGnU2mZe0RibNyjoEc2h05cYCT0cswGk1LWzMHic8TbrHg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">图 6： 模型推理过程中末端执行器轨迹记录图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">One More Thing：</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503522402\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"64\" style=\"width:34px;height:26px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=650456ac&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicGEnDGkLkVWt55aMUZK7UEr14yNCcpFFVAtlia3Y8bU53EzuQtHZxcUkjIf9ibkAhu0Pd4CO4Pv4Kg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">价值模型的零成本替代方案</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">最近，Physical Intelligence 的</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503522402\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"64\" style=\"width:34px;height:26px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=650456ac&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicGEnDGkLkVWt55aMUZK7UEr14yNCcpFFVAtlia3Y8bU53EzuQtHZxcUkjIf9ibkAhu0Pd4CO4Pv4Kg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\">&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通过 RL (RECAP) 带来的惊人能力提升，其技术核心在于基于模型的准确价值估计，而其技术实现需要针对每个任务收集数据、微调价值模型，这在多任务、少样本场景下极具挑战。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">我们发现，SRPO 是其零成本的代替方案，是一个「免费的午餐」</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503522403\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.916030534351145\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"393\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"306\" data-backh=\"586\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=75e27b32&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicGEnDGkLkVWt55aMUZK7UEcuuhrV9dZYP38qaOTdQJ0y1QtafP3vib1nQIPGOSbmnFnCChb7g1uicw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">图 7：</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503522402\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"64\" style=\"width:28px;height:21px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=650456ac&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicGEnDGkLkVWt55aMUZK7UEr14yNCcpFFVAtlia3Y8bU53EzuQtHZxcUkjIf9ibkAhu0Pd4CO4Pv4Kg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">&nbsp;与 SRPO 价值曲线对比。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">图 7 中的三个场景均取自&nbsp;</span><img data-imgfileid=\"503522402\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"64\" style=\"width:28px;height:21px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=650456ac&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gWicGEnDGkLkVWt55aMUZK7UEr14yNCcpFFVAtlia3Y8bU53EzuQtHZxcUkjIf9ibkAhu0Pd4CO4Pv4Kg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\">&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">官方主页，白色曲线是 PI 官方给出的价值曲线，而黄色曲线是我们的 SRPO 方法得到的价值曲线，可以看出，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">二者在趋势上高度相似，但我们的方法无需任何任务微调。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">结语</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">告别昂贵的数据标注和复杂的奖励设计，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">SRPO 仅凭模型自身的成功经验与物理世界常识，即可实现性能跃迁</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。无需训练价值模型，无需人工奖励工程，无需密集专家示范，SRPO 实现了让机器人从「模仿」走向「创造」，从「依赖」走向「自主」，为 VLA 强化学习开辟了一条充满希望的新路径。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "SRPO 框架通过自参考评估机制，无需专家数据和奖励工程，使机器人 VLA 模型在短短 200 步内，性能从 48.9%飙升至 99.2%，并展现出强大的泛化能力和自主寻路潜力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "SRPO 框架通过自参考评估机制，无需专家数据和奖励工程，使机器人 VLA 模型在短短 200 步内，性能从 48.9%飙升至 99.2%，并展现出强大的泛化能力和自主寻路潜力。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了复旦大学、同济大学与上海创智学院团队提出的自参考策略优化框架（SRPO），旨在解决 VLA 模型强化学习中对专家示范数据的高度依赖和奖励稀疏问题。SRPO 通过内部构建的自参照评估机制，利用模型自身生成的成功轨迹为失败尝试提供渐进式奖励，从而实现了无需外部专家数据注入或任务特定奖励工程的自适应策略优化。该框架在 LIBERO 榜单上取得了 99.2%的 SOTA 成功率，并在 LIBERO-Plus 泛化任务上性能暴涨 167%。SRPO 的核心技术方案包括同策略轨迹收集、基于潜在世界表征的轨迹聚类以及利用轨迹距离计算渐进式奖励，并将其整合到 PPO 风格的策略优化目标中。实验证明，SRPO 不仅大幅提升了训练效率和泛化能力，还能激发机器人探索专家轨迹之外的新策略。",
